This paper is about abstract interpretation of logic programs, which is a topic that falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses measuring precision of different analyses, which is a topic that falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes metrics for abstract domains, which is a topic that falls under formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL).
